{"tid":2104682,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"日劇腦殘番 - 忒修斯之船","createTime":"2020-07-12T06:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T18:52:31.000Z","uid":142772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"529b0fc4a0775e17ebc7f5467f225f0277212fb2","tid":2104682,"uid":142772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"因為日劇post 推介先睇，本身睇到一半到家姐幫佢奶奶個段想棄，個家姐竟然諗唔到佢奶奶想殺證人，仲要食粒不明來歷既藥，真係唔驚粒藥係墮胎藥，但我知咁早下判斷唔係咁好，所以睇埋落去，但劇情一次比一次腦殘，我睇完都唔知睇左咩，只係見到男主每次都話要阻止兇手但每次都越幫越忙，每次都中哂兇手既計，而家岩岩睇完身9集，我決定放棄，真係睇唔落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543abc9c87cd6aab44026335c4cc3ec4e86ae892","tid":2104682,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"睇錯家姐幫佢奶 差d想搵黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c2814f52014adf9bde33e963854f7dd336c057","tid":2104682,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾劇黎 睇漫畫好過"},{"pid":"c58690d77652bb1fc64b6d029e30714341e15873","tid":2104682,"uid":142772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"543abc9c87cd6aab44026335c4cc3ec4e86ae892","tid":2104682,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"睇錯家姐幫佢奶 差d想搵黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebadd3adfd8cec52eea342e7802591c61cb4695","tid":2104682,"uid":142772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c2814f52014adf9bde33e963854f7dd336c057","tid":2104682,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾劇黎 睇漫畫好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇"},{"pid":"e0da93a8f329c6c956e96f8320a507d66e05e05d","tid":2104682,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"